      {
        "name": "Life Drain",
        "text": "*Melee Weapon Attack:* ATK[DEX] to hit, reach 5 ft., one creature. *Hit:* DMG[4d8 + DEX] necrotic damage. The target must succeed on a DC 14 Constitution saving throw or its hit point maximum is reduced by an amount equal to the damage taken. This reduction lasts until the target finishes a long rest. The target dies if this effect reduces its hit point maximum to 0."
      },
      {
        "name": "Create Specter",
        "text": "[name] targets a humanoid within 10 feet of it that has been dead for no longer than 1 minute and died violently. The target's spirit rises as a specter in the space of its corpse or in the nearest unoccupied space. The specter is under [name]'s control. [name] can have no more than seven specters under its control at one time."
      }
    ]
